Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:02.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光の使者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:02.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光之使者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:04.27,Black,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord5\b0\be5}Cure Black
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.60,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光の使者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.60,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光之使者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.22,White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord5\b0\be5}Cure White
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ふたりはプリキュア！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我们两人是Precure！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:15.74,Default JP,,0,0,0,,闇の力の僕たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:15.74,Default CN,,0,0,0,,黑暗力量的奴仆们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,とっととお家に  帰りなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,还不快点给我滚回老家去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,邪魔だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いきなりなんてことすんのよ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你突然地干什么啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何をしたのだ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,一体...どうなってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,到底...是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,邪魔だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,别挡道！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何かがおかしい...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是哪里出问题了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.27,Default JP,,0,0,0,,こんなはずでは...！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.27,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不应该这样的...！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.60,Black,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord5\b0\be5}Black Thunder
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.87,White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord5\b0\be5}White Thunder
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:30.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,プリキュアの美しき魂が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:30.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,以Precure之美丽灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.49,Default JP,,0,0,0,,サーキュラス！何をしている？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.49,Default CN,,0,0,0,,萨库拉斯！你愣着干嘛？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,邪悪な心を打ち砕く！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,于此将邪恶之心粉碎！
